    "description": "Commerce One Holdings Inc. provides solutions for e-commerce business operators to start and operate their businesses in Japan. The company provides futureshop, a SaaS e-commerce platform that includes commerce creator. It also offers package software that allows for unified management of order and inventory for multiple e-commerce stores. In addition, the company provides ECnote, a self-developed EC order status bulletin viewer tool; Fast Connector, a middle software tool, that solves database-related issues; and CREAD, a solution that offers video and still image creative for a variety of platforms, including e-commerce sites, SNS, advertising, and web media. Additionally, it offers influencer marketing and social commerce services. Commerce One Holdings Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Chiyoda, Japan."
